2. cs.GR (Group Theory) - The paper discusses the action of a cyclic subgroup of the general linear group on subspaces, which is a topic in group theory. 
3. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) - The paper involves combinatorial constructions of codes and their properties, which is a topic in discrete mathematics. 
4. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) - The paper discusses the use of subfields to determine the cardinality and distance of codes, which is a topic in numerical analysis.
